OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA lot of dry and bright weather
OL,6,Fwith sunny interludes and light winds.
OL,7,FA chance of one or two light showers,
OL,8,Fespecially over northern counties in
OL,9,Fthe morning. Plenty of sunshine
OL,10,Fdeveloping this afternoon. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA settled evening with some
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Cloud will then
OL,14,Fincrease through the night to bring
OL,15,Fthe risk of patchy rain in the early
OL,16,Fhours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
