OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy morning
OL,6,Fwith patchy light rain which may
OL,7,Flinger in the west. The best of the
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter conditions will be
OL,9,Faround the Belfast area.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FBright but with good deal of cloud
OL,13,Faround during this period and a few
OL,14,Fshowers. Rather breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
